OL,3,CMan, woman and child die after falling
OL,4,Cfrom high-rise block of flats in London
OL,6,FA man, woman and a child have all died
OL,7,Fafter a fall from a high-rise block of
OL,8,Fflats in south London, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police has said.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,Fflats on Churchyard Row, Elephant and
OL,13,FCastle, at 7.29am on Wednesday,
OL,14,Ffollowing reports that people had
OL,15,Ffallen from height.
OL,17,FDespite resuscitation attempts by
OL,18,Femergency services personnel, the man,
OL,19,Fwoman and child were found to have
OL,20,Fdied at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
