OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780067468
OL,3,CMan, woman and child die after falling
OL,4,Cfrom high-rise block of flats in London
OL,6,FTheir deaths are being treated as
OL,7,Funexpected and the Met is
OL,8,Finvestigating, the force said, adding
OL,9,Fthat there were no other reported
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Met Police
OL,13,Fsaid: "Work is underway to formally
OL,14,Fidentify those who died. Their next-of-
OL,15,Fkin have been informed and are being
OL,16,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
