OL,3,CMan, woman and child die after falling
OL,4,Cfrom high-rise block of flats in London
OL,6,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We were called at
OL,8,F7.31am on Wednesday, May 27, to
OL,9,Freports of an incident on Churchyard
OL,10,FRow, SE11.
OL,12,F"We sent a number of resources to the
OL,13,Fscene including ambulance crews, a
OL,14,Fparamedic in a fast response car, an
OL,15,Fincident response officer and
OL,16,Fparamedics from our hazardous area
OL,17,Fresponse team (HART).
OL,19,F"We also dispatched a trauma team in a
OL,20,Fcar from London's Air Ambulance.
