OL,3,CMan, woman and child die after falling
OL,4,Cfrom high-rise block of flats in London
OL,6,F"Our first paramedic arrived in around
OL,7,Ffour minutes. Very sadly, despite the
OL,8,Fbest efforts of our crews, three
OL,9,Fpeople were pronounced dead at the
OL,10,Fscene."
OL,12,FPolice are urging any witnesses or
OL,13,Fanyone with information to get in
OL,14,Ftouch by calling 101, quoting CAD 1613/
OL,15,F27MAY.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
